  m_text: 'It is intended to accelerate development of applications targeting Microsoft
    HoloLens, Windows Mixed Reality immersive (VR) headsets and OpenVR platform.
    It enables rapid prototyping via in-editor simulation that allows you to see
    changes immediately. MRTK operates as an extensible framework that provides developers
    the ability to swap out core components.

